topLevelComment.text:
For anyone looking for the way to format the list of docker containers
"ID	{{.ID}}
NAME	{{.Names}}
IMAGE	{{.Image}}
PORTS	{{.Ports}}
COMMAND	{{.Command}}
CREATED	{{.CreatedAt}}
STATUS	{{.Status}}
"

The code at 44:20 is the following:
docker ps --format="ID	{{.ID}}
NAME	{{.Names}}
IMAGE	{{.Image}}
PORTS	{{.Ports}}
COMMAND	{{.Command}}
CREATED	{{.CreatedAt}}
STATUS	{{.Status}}
"

